{"tid":2217721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"10月1不如搞多次香港之路獅子山篇","createTime":"2020-09-25T15:46:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T14:07:15.000Z","uid":170819,"like":86,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"20e636e4f818b52a851f5c0fd55a15c139ead5f5","tid":2217721,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:46:24.000Z","msg":"由於民陣申請10月1號嘅大遊行被狗反對，當日若然繼續出嚟而被狗咬，一係就非法集結，一係国安法，再唔係加多條暴動罪搞死你。<br />\n<br />\n根據以往事例，而家基本上冇可能夠人。與其冒咁大風險，不如好似上年9月13號中秋節咁搞多次香港之路獅子山篇，用燈光同人鏈話比全世界聽，香港人團火仲未熄。要靚畫面有靚畫面，要不被捕亦都可以做到。<br />\n<br />\n抗爭形式唔應該繼續局限於遊行，有好多方法大家可能遺忘咗。如果大家同意10月1號可以用香港之路獅子山篇2.0代替遊行，麻煩幫我推上熱門。"},{"pid":"e6ee8d0dc0d728b882e6985a37a33b657b2d957f","tid":2217721,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f895995f86c58b3f0ec7534276c9c74d47fd55b6","tid":2217721,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c528f4c727dfe2f3099e940ac2a26112c134f8d","tid":2217721,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e6ee8d0dc0d728b882e6985a37a33b657b2d957f","tid":2217721,"uid":259812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:47:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4adc3092fe62713c4f71324eb06ad6e559a8db","tid":2217721,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2ab7d5f9b70544e7492349965d9576ca3aa153ed","tid":2217721,"uid":170819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7d05ebdd531b1466561bec